thread.title_full: Over 30,000 people expected to join 'inclusive' Portland Women's March after Donald Trump inauguration

author: Lizzy Acker | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: Over 30,000 people expected to join 'inclusive' Portland Women's March after Donald Trump inauguration
text: The original organizers of Portland's Women's March came under fire for allegedly silencing people of color and trans people. But the event's new Portland leadership wants to include everyone.
